# Configuration and sensitive data
# Real configs live in bot/config/*.yaml; *.yaml.example templates remain tracked.
# The legacy bot/config/config_*.json files were archived to old_function/config/ in
# the config 2.0 sprint (see REFACTORING_PROGRESS.md step 9) and are gitignored via
# the old_function/ rule below.
bot/config/*.yaml
*.pem
*.key
*.env

# Migration tooling products that carry real IDs (see REFACTORING_PLAN.md P1-6 step 0)
tools/migration_db_seed.json
tools/migration_report.md

# Archived configs under old_function/ must never return to git with real IDs
# (`.json.example` / `.yaml.example` are NOT matched and stay tracked as templates)
old_function/**/*.json
old_function/**/*.yaml

